```

**Top-Level Fields Reference:**

| Field | Required | Type | Purpose |
|-------|----------|------|---------|
| `id` | Yes | `string` | Canonical plugin ID (used in config as `plugins.entries.<id>`) |
| `channels` | No | `string[]` | Channel IDs owned by this plugin |
| `configSchema` | Yes | `object` | JSON Schema for plugin config validation |
| `enabledByDefault` | No | `true` | Marks plugin as auto-enabled (bundled plugins only) |
| `name` | No | `string` | Human-readable plugin name |
| `description` | No | `string` | Short summary |
| `version` | No | `string` | Informational version |
| `uiHints` | No | `Record<string, object>` | UI labels, placeholders, sensitivity hints |
| `providerAuthEnvVars` | No | `Record<string, string[]>` | Env vars for provider auth without booting plugin |
| `providerAuthChoices` | No | `object[]` | Onboarding/auth metadata |
| `contracts` | No | `object` | Static capability ownership (tools, providers, etc.) |

