## 2. FILE STRUCTURE FOR EACH CHANNEL PLUGIN

Every channel plugin follows this consistent structure:

```
<plugin-id>/
├── package.json                    # Standard npm package metadata
├── openclaw.plugin.json            # Plugin discovery manifest
