## PulseBoard Channel Plugin - Complete Implementation Plan

### Overview

This plan describes every file needed to implement `extensions/pulseboard/` as a new OpenClaw channel plugin. The plugin mirrors the IRC plugin's architecture exactly, adapted for PulseBoard's fictional WebSocket-based platform. All file paths are absolute; all imports use `.js` extensions per ESM convention.

