## Step-by-Step File Implementations

### 1. `extensions/pulseboard/package.json`

Mirrors `extensions/irc/package.json` exactly. No runtime `dependencies` (fictional client, no npm packages needed).

```json
{
  "name": "@openclaw/pulseboard",
  "version": "2026.4.1-beta.1",
  "description": "OpenClaw PulseBoard channel plugin",
  "type": "module",
  "devDependencies": {
